  "description": "<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?quality=85&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fcrop%3D1600%252C1065%252C0%252C0%26quality%3D85%26format%3Djpg%26resize%3D1600%252C1065%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-12%252Faadd10a0-21f5-11ea-b729-8e5754aac6ae%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D5322d053786d54a7a925a151582c8ca50d2f9e74&amp;client=amp-blogside-v2&amp;signature=9267d641ef31828cf4eaef2f6c2e8f538af765e2\" />\nLG 每年在 CES 上都会推出新款屏幕产品，今年也不例外了，而最新的一款更是搭载了多款的大热元素呢。这 32 吋的 UltraFine Ergo（32UN880）是款用上 4K IPS 面板的屏幕，重点是其专属的底座是可以让屏幕贴住墙壁，有 280 度水平平移，也有 25 度的俯角调整。自然也会支持单独一根 USB-C 线来同时传输电力和数据的用法，大大减少桌上的混乱。", 
